%#----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Setup
%#----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Prerequisites:

  * [Ruby] 1.8.6 or newer.

  * [RubyGems] 1.3.6 or newer.

  * [wmii] 3.9 or newer.

Installing:

    gem install rumai

Upgrading:

    gem update rumai

Removing:

    gem uninstall rumai
